  "title": "Shipping Officer",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>Job Description</strong></u></p><p>· Perform import and export shipping administration including transshipment</p><p>· Coordinate with insurance company on import/ export shipment’s cargo surveys and claim settlements</p><p>· Perform freight forwarding duties</p><p>· Coordinate and negotiate with banks on administrative compliance</p><p>· Prepare and provide other shipping administration and coordination support to internal departments</p><p>· Coordinate with Chambers of Commerce on the application of certificate of origin and Form-D</p><p>· Certify all compliance of Singapore Customs (Crimson logic) on the deduction of taxes and forwarders’ nominated declaration.</p><p><br /></p><p><u><strong>Job Requirements</strong></u></p><p>· Diploma in Shipping/Logistic or equivalent</p><p>· Min 1 year shipping and freight forwarding working experience</p><p>· Proficiency in computer skills (Microsoft Office)</p>",
